{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Worm Tooth","summaries":["<b>Worm Tooth</b> is a <linked>crafting material</linked> dropped by <linked>Devourers</linked> in <linked>The Corruption</linked>. It appears to be the tooth of the <linked>Devourers</linked>. Unlike most Corruption items, it does not have a <linked>Crimson</linked> equivalent, rendering its recipes uncraftable in a Crimson world prior to <linked>Hardmode</linked> without bringing over items from a Corrupt world. However, in Hardmode, when the <linked>Dryad</linked> is in the <linked>Graveyard biome</linked>, she sells the <linked>seeds</linked> of the world evil opposite of the current world evil (i.e. <linked>Corrupt Seeds</linked> in a Crimson world and <linked>Crimson Seeds</linked> in a Corrupt world). This means the player can create an artificial Corrupt biome in a Crimson world, and therefore allow Devourers to spawn and drop Worm Teeth."],"statistics":{"Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\"><linked>[img:Rarity level: 0]</linked></span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"20 Copper Coins\" data-sort-value=\"20\"><span class=\"cc\">20</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">25 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"<span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Used_in\">Used in</span>":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\"><linked>[img:Unholy Arrow]</linked><span><span><linked>Unholy Arrow</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(5)</span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Wooden Arrow]</linked><span><span><linked>Wooden Arrow</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(5)</span></li><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Worm Tooth]</linked><span><span><linked>Worm Tooth</linked></span></span></span></li></ul>"},"station":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Iron Anvil]</linked><span><span><linked>Iron Anvil</linked></span></span></span><br><i><b>or</b></i><br><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Lead An